data.description: Welcome to 27 Bass Lake Rd! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located in the serene neighborhood of Amston CT. This charming house offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. The first floor of this home features a large open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen features granite countertops, tiled backsplash and stainless steel appliances. There is also a bedroom and a remodeled full bathroom. Enjoy the large deck off the dining room for that morning cup of coffee. The 2nd floor of this house has 2 larger bedrooms and another completely remodeled bathroom. The lower level of this home has an additional 500 sq.ft. of living space. Enjoy the walkable distance to the picturesque lake, offering stunning views and recreational opportunities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this lovely home in Amston.
